<div class="page-header">
  <h1>Looks like your team is already using Boards.</h1>
</div> {{! .page-header }}

<p class="lead">A team called <strong>{{account}}</strong> has been set up which allows self-sign up for anyone who can verify a <strong>@{{domain}}</strong> address.</p>

<p class="lead">We'll send you an email to confirm you have access to the account and get you right in to your team's instance.</p>

<div class="form-group">
  <button type="button" class="btn btn-success" data-action="confirm">Send confirmation email</button>
  <div data-error="email" class="help-block"></div>
</div> {{! .form-group }}

<p><button type="button" class="btn btn-link" data-action="request">Request an invite</button> to create a new one.</p>
